title: 'This is history' -fans marvel at 'Black Panther' premiere
text:
'This is history' -fans marvel at 'Black Panther' premiere 6:19pm GMT - 00:56 
Donned in traditional African attire and superhero costumes, fans of the Disney/Marvel Studios 'Black Panther' movie flocked to theaters to view the first black superhero featured on the silver screen.
